name: Universe #299
description: Universe #299 - Rovom was a universe that was presumed destroyed by the lava that covered it. It was far from it's truth. The red and orange waters were host to amazing creatures of harmony and it's color was a protective illusion towards intruders. It's discovery was not wide, but also it wasn't in good faith either. 299 with it's aeons of knowledge saw this. Heartbroken, it broke it's slumber and helped the universe escape from the clutches of evil forever.
